## ğŸ—ƒï¸ How to Run

### 1. Clone the repo

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/stock-forecasting-project.git
cd stock-forecasting-project
```

### 2. Install requirements

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 3. Run Streamlit dashboard

```bash
