## ğŸŒ Deployment

You can deploy this app to Streamlit Cloud:

1. Push your project to a **public GitHub repo**
2. Go to [https://streamlit.io/cloud](https://streamlit.io/cloud) and connect your GitHub
3. Select `app.py` as the main file
4. Click **Deploy**
5. Share the generated link with your team ğŸŒ

